{"tid":2407661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉花樣年華look拍片　祝各位情人節開開心心，「像我手上的手工朱古力一樣甜甜蜜蜜」","createTime":"2021-02-14T08:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T08:57:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4760e9af1e60b3d798b9af2d64171f116d2c3bab","tid":2407661,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"今年情入節剛巧時大年初三「赤口」，中西節日撞日子下，新民黨主席葉劉淑儀亦有巧思，身穿鮮紅繡花旗袍的她，到了裝潢復古的西餐廳拍片，向情人送上祝福。乍看下與花樣年華中張曼玉與梁朝偉於茶餐廳用膳一幕，真有點似曾相識。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉在片中笑言情人們今天要「和和氣氣」，即使有爭吵也要「床頭打交床尾和」，相當暖心。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀在片段中說，今天是大年初三，也是情人節，有指「赤口」會容易吵架，所以特意溫馨提示情人們，今天要和和氣氣，不要吵架，即使偶有爭吵，亦應「床頭打交床尾和」。<br />\n<br />\n片末，葉劉拿起手中的一盒心形朱古力盒子，祝各位情人節開開心心，「像我手上的手工朱古力一樣甜甜蜜蜜」。<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210214/437592970246492160026471.png/25o6kO6Hb08o4a2lzv7xGj73E0bt5QDBqXH-gqlx_oI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210214%2F437592970246492160026471.png%2F25o6kO6Hb08o4a2lzv7xGj73E0bt5QDBqXH-gqlx_oI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=cb732fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210214/437592973560123392093615.png/kVSdbQO7nvGYD5m47zqWIWR3cNwhMd8rAhKiJwISoic?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210214%2F437592973560123392093615.png%2FkVSdbQO7nvGYD5m47zqWIWR3cNwhMd8rAhKiJwISoic%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6c1a613e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210214/437592847462436864295810.png/XPeMpIwVXUbcwRp5EFXynKGP_tR7W1LL9RCQNvUQkDY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210214%2F437592847462436864295810.png%2FXPeMpIwVXUbcwRp5EFXynKGP_tR7W1LL9RCQNvUQkDY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=3c1a5225&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210214/437592976403992576712903.png/34SMta_VeCQ3E-8Q_7ydBAMeMb4Onw4GhMxPQYTMT0E?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210214%2F437592976403992576712903.png%2F34SMta_VeCQ3E-8Q_7ydBAMeMb4Onw4GhMxPQYTMT0E%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f8546b8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78d9ea4d4f14154f8951024d7dc26c95b0b21f94","tid":2407661,"uid":282362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:27:14.000Z","msg":"𠵱啲就有圖"},{"pid":"bc4c85fc547afbbb150a1e51f0143f1c5bfb05b0","tid":2407661,"uid":48631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"呢個衰妹越大個囡越淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3f044e473911fc3b5c62af9e9bbb813430d339","tid":2407661,"uid":156652,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWQc0EN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWQc0EN.gif&h=59186753&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03b9cac22ed7203949610133bf7a94bf5fe988de","tid":2407661,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:31:17.000Z","msg":"姐姐一定著埋肚兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483e85ab752d6dcbd799163ee5435822b334b1ba","tid":2407661,"uid":81559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba3f044e473911fc3b5c62af9e9bbb813430d339","tid":2407661,"uid":156652,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWQc0EN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWQc0EN.gif&h=59186753&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f026f99c176f1e9fbb650b4e1c7e6c4076027e","tid"